{"tid":890593,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【第一滴血】太古城大劈價21% 三房1,180萬沽平過兩房","createTime":"2018-11-05T12:12:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T06:06:28.000Z","uid":174649,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"8feda511951a0335dde70dfaf69744ad09994201","tid":890593,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T12:12:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181105/large/1541412943_7af7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181105%2Flarge%2F1541412943_7af7.jpg&h=5a2c5059&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n樓市淡靜，龍頭屋苑鰂魚涌太古城也罕見大劈價。<br />\n<br />\n美聯物業吳肇基表示，太古城本月首宗成交即「流血」，三房變兩房價出售。單位為高安閣中層B室，實用面積701方呎，三房間隔，今年8月放盤叫價1,550萬元，累減270萬至近期1,280萬元仍未有買家承接，直至剛剛減多100萬元，至1,180萬元低市價兩成終易手，呎價僅16,833元。<br />\n<br />\n代理表示，同座低層C室，也是701方呎，今年8月以1,380萬元成交，未計樓層因素已賣平200萬元。如以3月成交的高安閣中層C室造價1,500萬元比較，更平足320萬元或21%。而太古城兩房造價高峯期曾升至逾1,300萬元。"},{"pid":"bfd950d00218065172fe30c241db4567b759ece1","tid":890593,"uid":114064,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T12:14:51.000Z","msg":"太古城唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff3d6b18744f9f576c7d67ceeb72f18e4a542c9","tid":890593,"uid":146805,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bfd950d00218065172fe30c241db4567b759ece1","tid":890593,"uid":114064,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T12:14:51.000Z","msg":"太古城唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T12:15:35.000Z","msg":"跌價唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0495b110823fdca1c825e693bc56132b35bb7ad9","